Analysis and Studies (SAS) Panels and NATO assessment of intermediate force capabilities in appropriate allied
scenarios and exercises.
- Complete interaction with Combatant Commander Staffs to evaluate emerging intermediate force capabilities
and their utility in theater operations and Defense of the Homeland missions.
- Complete program management support for Joint and Allied Exercise, Experimentation, Demonstration, and
Assessment efforts.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
- Continue to assess the utility, effect, and effectiveness of technologies for incapacitating personnel, clearing
