encouraged to submit proposals that involve multi-component collaboration with Joint Services, International partners, and other government agencies. Proposals should
target one or more of the four key supporting concepts of the Joint Warfighting Concept: Joint Concept for Fires, Joint Concept for Command and Control, Joint Concept
for Contested Logistics, and Joint Concept for Information Advantage.

