D. Acquisition Strategy
The Navy awarded a sole source contract to KDA (NSM manufacturer) for production that started in FY 2024. This contract includes engineering services for system
improvements. In FY 2025, the Marine Corps leveraged the engineering services support on this contract, along with design and test support from government labs. As
sub-systems are matured, they will transition into the NSM production baseline for common production across both the Navy and Marine Corps.




