A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
The AM program focuses on development and use of AM equipment for Naval applications in land-based and afloat applications, including system performance
requirements, shipboard integration requirements and considerations, material selection, design optimization, equipment and component certification, and digital
engineering integration. Efforts also include consideration of AM across a wide variety of potential applications ensuring AM manufactured components can meet
mission requirements and that system/component technical requirements are updated to leverage AM.

