- Continue maturing 3D printed part candidacy tools in development in order to assess USMC equipment
programs in sustainment for printable parts, as well as evaluating future USMC programs under development
and assessment for percentage of parts that can be 3D printed to support sustainment operations in the field and
garrison.
- Continue the use of additive manufacturing and advanced manufacturing in the use of fabricating circuit boards
in expeditionary environments.
