Lab consists of a fast-valve operated Mach 6 Ludwieg Tube Wind Tunnel, a High Temperature Shock Tunnel
designed for combustion research, and a multi-purpose Blow-down Mach 3 Tunnel designed to study shock-
boundary layer interactions.

