Title: NREIP/SEAP                                                                                                   0.926        0.000       0.000      0.000       0.000
Description: This program supports both the Naval Research Enterprise Intern Program (NREIP) for college
students and the Science and Engineering Apprenticeship Program (SEAP) for high school students to
encourage participants to pursue science and engineering careers. The objective is to further education via
mentoring by laboratory personnel and their participation in research, and to make them aware of Department
of the Navy (DON) research and technology efforts. This program serves as a recruitment tool for employment
