D. Acquisition Strategy
The USV Enabling Capabilities initiative will accelerate the Navy's USV capabilities to meet current and future operational demands. By strategically integrating
commercial solutions and Department of Defense research and development innovations, this initiative will deliver advanced capabilities and payloads tailored to the
Fleet's requirements. This approach will eliminate redundancies, foster innovation, and strengthen coordination across the USV FoS. The initiative directly supports

